in three different places.

13:18.631 --> 13:20.842
They had to airlift me
off the fucking field.

13:20.925 --> 13:23.428
Watch your fucking mouth.

13:23.511 --> 13:25.805
Just... I just need
a little time.

13:25.889 --> 13:28.016
I'm paying child support
to Brook,

13:28.099 --> 13:29.976
to Janelle, to Sharise.

13:30.060 --> 13:31.770
I'm doing everything I can.

13:31.853 --> 13:33.563
Everything but a vasectomy.

13:33.605 --> 13:35.231
(laughs)

13:35.273 --> 13:37.442
What you laughing at,
Mr. Mafioso?

13:37.484 --> 13:39.110
Oh, I'm not mafioso.

13:39.152 --> 13:41.946
That's right. Mafiosos
pay off their grandma's house.

13:41.988 --> 13:44.366
They take care of the people
who raised them.

13:44.449 --> 13:47.827
I will not rest until I get you
back into a beautiful home.

13:47.911 --> 13:49.954
Good.

13:52.374 --> 13:55.377
Hmm. Does this thing have HBO?

13:55.460 --> 13:57.212
Just basic cable.

13:57.295 --> 14:01.257
How am I supposed to see
all that dragon shit?

14:04.469 --> 14:05.512
I'll get on it.

14:05.595 --> 14:08.640
See that you do. And you...

14:10.016 --> 14:11.476
You look awful.

14:11.559 --> 14:13.228
I know.

14:14.688 --> 14:17.357
-(laughs)
-What?

14:17.440 --> 14:20.151
"The dragon shit."

14:21.820 --> 14:23.822
What the fuck?

14:23.905 --> 14:26.491
Yo, what happened to our car?

14:26.574 --> 14:27.992
Got repoed, man.

14:28.076 --> 14:30.495
But I was watching.

14:30.578 --> 14:32.205
Repoed?

14:32.288 --> 14:34.708
Didn't you take that car
in a trade?

14:34.790 --> 14:37.293
Yeah, the Blue Book
was twice what he owed us.

14:37.335 --> 14:39.170
Oh, man.

14:40.463 --> 14:42.841
-I guess we're taking your car.
-I can't.

14:42.924 --> 14:45.051
Grandma needs it
to go to water aerobics.

14:45.135 --> 14:47.220
Are you kidding me?
Does she have to?

14:47.303 --> 14:49.055
Do you want to go back in there

14:49.139 --> 14:51.933
and tell her she can't go?

14:54.811 --> 14:55.895
What you doing?

14:55.979 --> 14:57.689
