14:57.731 --> 14:59.691
No, take a Lyft.
Got a gift card.

14:59.774 --> 15:02.986
Really? Who gives you
a gift card for Lyft?

15:03.028 --> 15:05.530
-You did, Danny.
-Oh.

15:05.572 --> 15:07.574
You're welcome.

15:07.657 --> 15:09.492
(sighs)

