I'm good.

16:03.713 --> 16:05.131
Are you happy with this?

16:05.215 --> 16:06.758
What do you want me to do?

16:06.800 --> 16:10.053
Eh, you could start
by tightening the man spread.

16:10.095 --> 16:12.347
(sighs)

16:12.430 --> 16:14.265
HECTOR:
You don't recognize me, do you?

16:14.307 --> 16:16.851
I can't really see
from back here.

16:16.935 --> 16:20.105
It's me, Hector.
"Hector delivers."

16:20.188 --> 16:23.775
Oh, sure, the pot guy.

16:23.817 --> 16:25.193
-Danny, right?
-Yeah.

16:25.276 --> 16:27.904
Your wife enjoyed...

16:27.946 --> 16:30.532
Don't tell me.

16:30.615 --> 16:32.242
Purple OG Kush.

16:32.283 --> 16:35.203
Shit. That saved my marriage
a couple of times.

16:35.286 --> 16:37.205
What the hell
are you driving a Lyft for?

16:37.288 --> 16:38.790
Maybe you didn't notice.

16:38.832 --> 16:40.125
The pendejos in Sacramento
legalized pot.

16:40.165 --> 16:41.292
Put me out of business.

16:41.376 --> 16:42.919
Yeah, I'm sorry, man.

16:42.961 --> 16:44.295
Not as sorry as I am.

16:44.337 --> 16:46.089
-You still running a book?
-Yeah.

16:46.131 --> 16:47.674
Well, then you're next.

16:47.757 --> 16:49.342
Only a matter of time
before California

16:49.426 --> 16:50.885
legalizes sports betting.

16:50.969 --> 16:53.304
Nah, the Indian casinos
will never let it happen.

16:53.346 --> 16:55.390
Oh, sure, government
never fucks over Indians.

16:55.473 --> 16:58.476
Hang on, excuse me one second.

17:03.148 --> 17:04.482
What are we stopping for?

17:04.566 --> 17:07.277
Don't worry.
I'm not on the clock.

17:22.041 --> 17:23.542
BOTH:
Oh!

17:27.380 --> 17:29.299
(bat clatters in trunk)

17:36.181 --> 17:39.100
Okay...

17:39.184 --> 17:41.019
Back on the clock.

17:41.102 --> 17:42.395
So, Danny,

17:42.479 --> 17:44.105
