17:57.494 --> 18:00.288
♪ If you're not into yoga ♪

18:00.372 --> 18:03.041
♪ If you have half a brain ♪

18:03.875 --> 18:06.795
♪ If you like makin' love
at midnight ♪

18:06.878 --> 18:10.298
♪ In the dunes on the cape... ♪

18:10.382 --> 18:11.633
DANNY:
Can you wait?

18:11.716 --> 18:14.344
-Your gift card.
-RAY: Be right back.

18:14.386 --> 18:16.513
♪ Write to me and escape... ♪

18:21.976 --> 18:24.104
Hi. Welcome to Freedom
from Bondage House.

18:24.187 --> 18:25.230
How can I help you?

18:25.271 --> 18:26.731
