25:26.401 --> 25:27.819
I got a brother who's a dentist.

25:27.861 --> 25:30.113
He showed me pictures.
Can't be a part of that.

25:30.155 --> 25:31.322
DANNY:
Oh.

25:31.406 --> 25:33.116
RAY:
That's... that's noble.

25:33.158 --> 25:35.452
I don't know about noble, but
at least I can sleep at night.

25:35.493 --> 25:37.412
After I smoke a bowl,
rub one out.

25:37.495 --> 25:39.956
(laughter)

25:41.666 --> 25:44.210
Oh, I got to do a toast.

25:44.294 --> 25:45.837
To a shitty day

25:45.879 --> 25:48.006
that turned into
a really great day.

25:48.048 --> 25:50.550
-Hear, hear. Ah.
-Salud. Salud.

25:50.633 --> 25:52.177
DANNY: You mind if I sit
in the front seat?

25:52.218 --> 25:53.595
Be my guest.

25:53.678 --> 25:54.846
Not that I didn't enjoy
our inadvertent

25:54.929 --> 25:56.431
dry hump in the back.

25:56.514 --> 25:57.849
RAY (laughs): Hey,
just get your ass in the car.

25:57.891 --> 25:59.142
Give me the watch.

26:00.226 --> 26:01.811
Oh, fuck.

26:01.853 --> 26:03.355
Come on, give me
the fucking watch.

26:03.396 --> 26:05.148
And if I don't,
are you really gonna shoot me?

26:05.190 --> 26:06.858
RAY: It's not worth it, Danny.
Just give him the watch.

26:06.941 --> 26:08.234
But what about our bad day
turning into a good day?

26:08.318 --> 26:10.195
Don't make me
fucking kill you, man.

26:10.278 --> 26:11.363
Shit.

26:11.446 --> 26:13.281
-(sighs)
-What're you doing, Ray?

26:13.365 --> 26:14.366
Yeah, what're you doing?

26:14.449 --> 26:15.658
Protecting the quarterback.

26:15.700 --> 26:16.785
-What?
-Throw the ball, Danny.

26:16.868 --> 26:19.704
-What?
-Throw the ball.

26:19.746 --> 26:21.039
DANNY:
Oh.

26:25.543 --> 26:27.545
Anything?

26:27.587 --> 26:29.547
You hit him once.

26:29.589 --> 26:30.840
Oh, Jesus.

26:30.882 --> 26:32.258
